OL,3,C15 people have died after getting into
OL,4,Ctrouble in open water during heatwave
OL,6,FA 13-year-old girl has died in North
OL,7,FYorkshire, and search efforts continue
OL,8,Ffor a boy who is missing after going
OL,9,Finto a river in South Yorkshire,
OL,10,Ftaking the number of water-related
OL,11,Fdeaths during the recent hot weather
OL,12,Fto 15.
OL,14,FThe teenage girl was pulled from the
OL,15,FRiver Wharfe in Burnsall, near
OL,16,FSkipton, on Sunday evening. She was
OL,17,Fairlifted to the hospital but was
OL,18,Flater pronounced dead, North Yorkshire
OL,19,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
