OL,3,C15 people have died after getting into
OL,4,Ctrouble in open water during heatwave
OL,6,FIn South Yorkshire, officers said the
OL,7,Fsearch had entered a second day for an
OL,8,F11-year-old boy who went into the
OL,9,FRiver Don on Saturday and has not been
OL,10,Fseen since.
OL,12,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,13,FFerry Boat Lane in Mexborough at
OL,14,Faround 8pm on Saturday.
OL,16,FEmergency crews from the National
OL,17,FPolice Air Service, Yorkshire
OL,18,FAmbulance Service and the South
OL,19,FYorkshire Fire and Rescue Services
OL,20,Falso responded, North Yorkshire Police
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
