CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780405873
OL,3,C15 people have died after getting into
OL,4,Ctrouble in open water during heatwave
OL,6,FThe boy has not yet been found, and
OL,7,Fhis family is being supported by
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FIn a statement on Monday morning, the
OL,11,Fforce said: "We understand people are
OL,12,Fdesperate to help but, for everyone's
OL,13,Fsafety, we must ask that only those
OL,14,Finvolved in our operation join the
OL,15,Fsearch."
OL,17,FSo far, those reported to have died in
OL,18,Fwater incidents are:
