OL,3,C15 people have died after getting into
OL,4,Ctrouble in open water during heatwave
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Royal Life Saving Society (RLSS)
OL,12,Fissued a warning following the deaths,
OL,13,Fsaying it sees a "heightened risk of
OL,14,Fdrowning when air temperatures are
OL,15,Fhigher".
OL,17,FThis all comes as temperatures dropped
OL,18,Ftowards the average for the time of
OL,19,Fyear following the heatwave.
