OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780405873
OL,3,C15 people have died after getting into
OL,4,Ctrouble in open water during heatwave
OL,6,FMay 26 was the hottest day in May on
OL,7,Frecord for both England and Wales,
OL,8,Fwith 35.1C measured at Kew Gardens and
OL,9,F32.9C at Cardiff Bute Park.
OL,11,FMet Office meteorologist Rebecca
OL,12,FMitchell said the heatwave was "over".
OL,14,F"Ironically, it's the first week of
OL,15,Fmeteorological summer starting (on
OL,16,FMonday), but it will be feeling much
OL,17,Fmore like spring or autumn and a big
OL,18,Fcontrast to the heatwave," she said.
